data.text:
@HeyShawnHanna Yep. It's over, but not really.
Haven't had a day of worldwide deaths under 3,974 in nearly two years. Might finally get a few later this month.
@opiateofblame Could be. Just went out to dinner. It was weird. 15% masked. Most acting like it's gone.

@dumbassgenius I looked at the SF numbers today and it’s almost completely gone. To the point where I’m not sure I even trust the numbers. I think people are self testing and not reporting so it’s artificially down.
@dumbassgenius One would imagine that the widespread perception that 'it's over' is directly related to this trend.
